HEADWORD: Gamashes
<hw>Ga*mash"es</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>gamaches</ets>.]</ety> <def>High boots or buskins; in Scotland,
short spatterdashes or riding trousers, worn over the other
clothing.</def>⟦br⟧
